Sets the Vertical Blank IRQ routine on the Amiga. This method will then be called
once per frame.
<p>
Example:

<code>
procedure Update();
begin

    // .. do some IRQ update stuff
end;

begin
    // Sets the IRQ routine to "Update"
    vbirq(Update());
    // Turns on VB IRQ interrupts
    EnableInterrupt(VB_IRQ);
    ...
</code>


